`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
`clearAllChunkDiffs()` must be called BEFORE `gameState$.set()` in `performPrestige` — the chunk diffs live in a separate Legend State observable (`chunkDiffs$`) from the game store. The gameState$.set() only resets player stats; chunk deltas need their own explicit clear since the new world seed makes all previous deltas meaningless (the chunks they reference don't exist in the new procedurally-generated world).

`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`

